PRIVACY NOTICE

SchoolDesk stores all user data (timetables, tasks, memos, checklists,
student names, etc.) locally on the user's machine. No data is transmitted
to external servers. No analytics, tracking, or advertising code is
included.

Data location: %APPDATA%\SchoolDesk\ (Windows)
                ~/Library/Application Support/SchoolDesk/ (macOS)

When personal information (e.g., student names) is entered, users are
responsible for:
- Using the app only on personal/secured computers
- Deleting the data folder when uninstalling
- Complying with the personal information protection laws and policies
  of their organization (school, district, etc.)
